[Student "S"]
{EAST has 15 points, and when North overcalls 2\H in front 
of her she has a perfect Negative Double - showing both of the Minor suits.

WEST doesn't like the Minor suits, but he has stoppers in \Hs, so 
he bids 2NT.

EAST is more than happy to raise to 3NT.}

